Class SoundfontInstrumentsTableModel

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel

    public class SoundfontInstrumentsTableModel
extends MidicaTableModel

    This class represents the data model of the soundfont instruments and drumkits table in the configuration details view of the info window.

    Each row represents either a category or a certain instrument or drum kit.

    A category can be one of the following:

    • Chromatic instruments
    • Single channel drum kits
    • Multi channel drum kits
    • Unknown

    The bank column is special. A bank can consist of 2 bytes. However in most cases only the MSB is used. In these cases we show only the MSB. If the LSB is not 0, we show both, MSB and LSB, separated by the currently configured separator bank separator syntax element.
